
Installation of IUCR templates
==============================

1) Grab the files iucr.cls and iucr.bst 
   from http://journals.iucr.org/d/services/authorservices.html
   
2) Copy the files to the following directories
   ~/texmf/tex/latex/iucr/iucr.cls
   ~/texmf/bibtex/bst/iucr.bst
   
3) Run texhash on the ~/texmf directory

Building this document
======================

Document needs to be built (to pdf) by the following commands
latex dxtbx.tex
bibtex dxtbx.aux
latex dxtbx.tex
latex dxtbx.tex
dvipdf dxtbx.dvi

This is done automatically by typing make
